   <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="diagnosis">
      <p>
Diagnosis
(modified from 

Smol 
et al.
2014

)
</p>
      <p>Only dorsolateral orthometanemes, ventral gland when present confined within pharyngeal region. Amphideal fovea and aperture variable but amphideal aperture never elongated, precloacal supplements (when present) papilliform, in single ventral row. Females monodelphic-opisthodelphic.</p>
